description:
As an admin user
  I want to manage sales
  So that I can create, view, and delete sales records

elements.name: Verify the functionality of navigating to the Sell Plant page

steps.name: the admin is logged in to the system
the admin navigates to the Sales page
the system should allow the admin to click on Sell Plant
the system should redirect to the Sell Plant page

elements.name: Verify the functionality of mandatory field validation on Sell Plant page

steps.name: the admin is logged in to the system
the admin navigates to the Sales page
the admin navigates to Sell Plant page
the admin leaves fields empty and clicks Sell
the system should show validation for plant selection
the system should display "Value must be greater than or equal to 1."

elements.name: Verify the functionality of the Plant dropdown displaying current stock

steps.name: the admin is logged in to the system
the admin navigates to the Sales page
the admin navigates to Sell Plant page
the admin clicks on Plant dropdown
the system should display a list of available plants
the system should display current stock for each plant

elements.name: Verify the functionality of the delete confirmation prompt

steps.name: the admin is logged in to the system
the admin navigates to the Sales page
the admin clicks on Delete for a sale record
the system should display a confirmation prompt before deletion

elements.name: Verify the functionality of recording a sale successfully

steps.name: the admin is logged in to the system
the admin navigates to the Sales page
the admin navigates to Sell Plant page
the admin selects a Plant
the admin enters Quantity "2"
the admin clicks on Sell
the system should reduce the stock
the system should redirect to the sales list

name: Sales Module - Admin Tests
